  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the thrilling world of <strong>Crazy Robot Ball</strong>, the ultimate turn-based football showdown! Take command of a team of high-tech robots, each with unique attributes designed to give you the edge in the battle for robotic football supremacy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gameplay Highlights:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Turn-Based Tactics:</u> Plan your moves strategically in this turn-based twist on traditional soccer. Anticipate your opponent’s plays, set up the perfect pass, and unleash unstoppable shots on goal!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3400150/extras/21e95246e87c4fd13c50d1da6e7ce295.poster.avif?t=1771673259\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3400150/extras/21e95246e87c4fd13c50d1da6e7ce295.webm?t=1771673259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3400150/extras/21e95246e87c4fd13c50d1da6e7ce295.mp4?t=1771673259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Customizable Robots:</u> Assemble your dream team with robots that boast specialized attributes such as lightning-fast speedsters to dart past defenders, powerhouse strikers to blast through any blockade, and durable defenders to hold the line.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3400150/extras/267af1bf1fdcec0222579db791b73d66.poster.avif?t=1771673259\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3400150/extras/267af1bf1fdcec0222579db791b73d66.webm?t=1771673259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3400150/extras/267af1bf1fdcec0222579db791b73d66.mp4?t=1771673259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Four Unique Maps:</u> Play across four distinct maps, each set in a unique location and featuring interesting layouts that add new layers of strategy. Adapt to varying terrain and field shapes to outwit your opponents.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3400150/extras/0368660b85a5371041d84fd8f3f970d1.poster.avif?t=1771673259\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3400150/extras/0368660b85a5371041d84fd8f3f970d1.webm?t=1771673259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3400150/extras/0368660b85a5371041d84fd8f3f970d1.mp4?t=1771673259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Game Modes for Every Player:</u> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Freeplay Mode:</u> Explore the game at your own pace. Experiment with lineups, perfect your strategies, and refine your skills without the pressure of competition.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Tournament Mode:</u> Test your mettle in a high-stakes championship. Face off against increasingly formidable opponents to claim the prestigious Golden Trophy and cement your legacy as a Crazy Robot Ball champion.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3400150/extras/9b0c49695d36606a432c89f362aaade8.poster.avif?t=1771673259\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3400150/extras/9b0c49695d36606a432c89f362aaade8.webm?t=1771673259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3400150/extras/9b0c49695d36606a432c89f362aaade8.mp4?t=1771673259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With vibrant arenas and dynamic play-by-play action, <strong>Crazy Robot Ball</strong> delivers an electrifying mix of strategy and excitement. Whether you're a casual gamer looking for a fun challenge or a tactical mastermind aiming to dominate the league, this game guarantees hours of thrilling gameplay.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the thrilling world of <strong>Crazy Robot Ball</strong>, the ultimate turn-based football showdown! Take command of a team of high-tech robots, each with unique attributes designed to give you the edge in the battle for robotic football supremacy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gameplay Highlights:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Turn-Based Tactics:</u> Plan your moves strategically in this turn-based twist on traditional soccer. Anticipate your opponent’s plays, set up the perfect pass, and unleash unstoppable shots on goal!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3400150/extras/21e95246e87c4fd13c50d1da6e7ce295.poster.avif?t=1771673259\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3400150/extras/21e95246e87c4fd13c50d1da6e7ce295.webm?t=1771673259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3400150/extras/21e95246e87c4fd13c50d1da6e7ce295.mp4?t=1771673259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Customizable Robots:</u> Assemble your dream team with robots that boast specialized attributes such as lightning-fast speedsters to dart past defenders, powerhouse strikers to blast through any blockade, and durable defenders to hold the line.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3400150/extras/267af1bf1fdcec0222579db791b73d66.poster.avif?t=1771673259\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3400150/extras/267af1bf1fdcec0222579db791b73d66.webm?t=1771673259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3400150/extras/267af1bf1fdcec0222579db791b73d66.mp4?t=1771673259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Four Unique Maps:</u> Play across four distinct maps, each set in a unique location and featuring interesting layouts that add new layers of strategy. Adapt to varying terrain and field shapes to outwit your opponents.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3400150/extras/0368660b85a5371041d84fd8f3f970d1.poster.avif?t=1771673259\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3400150/extras/0368660b85a5371041d84fd8f3f970d1.webm?t=1771673259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3400150/extras/0368660b85a5371041d84fd8f3f970d1.mp4?t=1771673259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Game Modes for Every Player:</u> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Freeplay Mode:</u> Explore the game at your own pace. Experiment with lineups, perfect your strategies, and refine your skills without the pressure of competition.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Tournament Mode:</u> Test your mettle in a high-stakes championship. Face off against increasingly formidable opponents to claim the prestigious Golden Trophy and cement your legacy as a Crazy Robot Ball champion.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3400150/extras/9b0c49695d36606a432c89f362aaade8.poster.avif?t=1771673259\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3400150/extras/9b0c49695d36606a432c89f362aaade8.webm?t=1771673259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3400150/extras/9b0c49695d36606a432c89f362aaade8.mp4?t=1771673259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With vibrant arenas and dynamic play-by-play action, <strong>Crazy Robot Ball</strong> delivers an electrifying mix of strategy and excitement. Whether you're a casual gamer looking for a fun challenge or a tactical mastermind aiming to dominate the league, this game guarantees hours of thrilling gameplay.</p>",
